    "description": "一对兄妹的回忆，都深埋在一个个梦境里。<br>而每一个梦境，都勾勒出不为人知的秘密。<br>这是一段救赎和被救赎的幻想旅程。<br>让我们，身披万丈光芒遁入无尽黑暗！<br><br>在苍茫的天地间体验一场精彩绝伦的冒险旅程。从群山之巅到峡谷深处，从大海之滨到隐秘回廊，观察线索，解开独有的创新性谜题，用手中的剑与脑海中的智慧来挑战不可一世的巨大敌人。谁能够穿透梦境的层层迷雾，发现出人意料的真相？<br><br>官方QQ群：562066807<br>微博：队友游戏<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857950/extras/e1b7c1d80611af8f658822a8d626001a.poster.avif?t=1694661004\" width=506 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857950/extras/e1b7c1d80611af8f658822a8d626001a.webm?t=1694661004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857950/extras/e1b7c1d80611af8f658822a8d626001a.mp4?t=1694661004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>游戏特色</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857950/extras/c41cac2db1d752510ccf7a67a04ce1c6.poster.avif?t=1694661004\" width=560 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857950/extras/c41cac2db1d752510ccf7a67a04ce1c6.webm?t=1694661004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857950/extras/c41cac2db1d752510ccf7a67a04ce1c6.mp4?t=1694661004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>有趣巧妙的谜题</strong><br><br>拥有7个不同风格关卡，每个关卡大量丰富的谜题。所有的谜题都是通过关卡环境结构产生的。玩家需要通过思考，利用现实中的物理、机关，与环境产生逻辑联系，来解开环境谜题。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857950/extras/5384c17a1ed8a3d8b9ea14d1f9cbc82f.poster.avif?t=1694661004\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857950/extras/5384c17a1ed8a3d8b9ea14d1f9cbc82f.webm?t=1694661004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857950/extras/5384c17a1ed8a3d8b9ea14d1f9cbc82f.mp4?t=1694661004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>以巧取胜的Boss战</strong><br><br>拥有8个精彩独特的Boss战。游戏中Boss战的最大特色是“只能智取，不可强攻”，玩家必须通过思考Boss的特点，让其弱点暴露，并利用时机对其进行有效打击，以巧克刚，战胜比自己强大的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857950/extras/50d0f6aa479e5ac3c8e7b8c5107e5cd0.poster.avif?t=1694661004\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857950/extras/50d0f6aa479e5ac3c8e7b8c5107e5cd0.webm?t=1694661004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/857950/extras/50d0f6aa479e5ac3c8e7b8c5107e5cd0.mp4?t=1694661004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>寻找尘封的记忆</strong><br><br>游戏中有许多隐藏的宝箱，他们通常放在不易发觉的地方。打开这些宝箱，玩家就可以发现主角记忆中的点点滴滴，收集这些记忆，揭开他们的故事和秘密。<br><br>预计完整游戏时长15小时。",
